Package api

Contains interface/abstract class definition of all needed classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Computer
    Computer interface is exposed to Computer and Space.
    Server
    Server Interface exposed to Universe and Client
    Space
    Space interface is exposed to both Computer and Client.
    Universe
    Universe Interface is exposed to Server and Space.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Client<T,A>
    Client Abstract Class
    Result
    Result is for containing result of a task execution, including the result Id, task start time and end time.
    Task<T>
    Task is a data structure containing a task to be executed by Computer.
